edu.fau.neighborhoodpocket

Class SuspiciousActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.fau.neighborhoodpocket.SuspiciousActivity

  • public class SuspiciousActivity
extends java.lang.Object
    Author:
    group1 This class is used to model a SuspiciousActivity. A SuspiciousActivity object is created whenever a user reports a suspicious activity. This class encapsulates different attributes that make up a Suspicious Activity.
